OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FAfter his story was featured on ITV
OL,7,FGranada Reports, the family were moved
OL,8,Finto hotel accommodation and told
OL,9,Fthere was a property they could move
OL,10,Finto that is being adapted to their
OL,11,Fneeds.
OL,13,FIt is a four-bedroomed house and
OL,14,Fassessments will be carried out on
OL,15,Fwhether seven-year-old Harry, who has
OL,16,Fcerebral palsy, will be able to use
OL,17,Fthe stairlift to access a wet room or
OL,18,Fif an adapted lift will be needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
