OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FStephen said he had been "despairing"
OL,7,Fliving in the cramped flat in Widnes,
OL,8,FCheshire, and worried about how long
OL,9,Fhe would be able to carry Harry
OL,10,Fupstairs.
OL,12,F"Within 24 hours our situation had
OL,13,Fchanged", Stephen said. "We were moved
OL,14,Fto a hotel and told the property we
OL,15,Fhad wanted, was going to be ours and
OL,16,Fwas being adapted.
OL,18,F"It is close to the children's school
OL,19,Fand we can start moving forwards with
OL,20,Four lives'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
