OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FA Halton Housing spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Since the change in Mr Murray's
OL,8,Fcircumstances we have continued to
OL,9,Fwork tirelessly alongside other
OL,10,Fagencies to find an alternative home
OL,11,Ffor Mr Murray and his family.
OL,13,F"We are pleased to confirm that a
OL,14,Fsuitable property has now been
OL,15,Fidentified and is currently being
OL,16,Fadapted to meet this family's specific
OL,17,Fneeds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
