OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FHe added: "While I am very pleased
OL,7,Fthat Stephen and the children are no
OL,8,Flonger living in the appalling
OL,9,Fconditions that they were, questions
OL,10,Fremain about how it was allowed to
OL,11,Fcontinue for so long.
OL,13,F"I have asked those questions and
OL,14,Fawait the results and the report of
OL,15,Fthe inquiry that is ongoing into this
OL,16,Fcase.I wish Stephen and his children
OL,17,Fevery happiness in their new home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
